  <h1>What is Grab Food?</h1>
  <p>Grab Food is a feature under the Grab App where you can order food from restaurants all over singapore to deliver to your desired destination. It is a free app service for everyone.</p>

  <h2 id="Inst">Installation Guide!</h2>
  <p>**Steps to use Grab app:**</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Download and install the Grab app on your mobile phone.<br> Please click "Get it On Google Play" if you're an Android user, otherwise <br> click "Download on the Apple Store".</li>
    <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.grabtaxi.passenger&hl=en&gl=US"><img src="/images/For-Logos/to_google_play_store.png" width="180" height="70"></a>
    <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/grab-taxi-ride-food-delivery/id647268330"><img src="/images/For-Logos/to_apple_store.png" width="180" height="60"></a>
    <p></p>
  </ol>

  <h2 id = "req">Requirements</h2>
      <p>Make sure you have your Grab app downloaded. Select the Food icon to view grab Food features.</p>
      <img src = "/images/Grab/maingrabpage.jpg" width = "300px"><br><br>

  <h2 id = "Ordering">Ordering Meals</h2>
    <p>Press on the search bar to find the restaurant you want to order food from</p>
    <img src="/images/Grab/FoodMain.jpg" width="300px"><br><br>
    <p>
        Select the search bar and key in the restaurant you wish to order from and it will show up along with restaurants similar to it
    </p>
    <img src="/images/Grab/RestCat.jpg" width="300px"><br><br>
    <p>Select the meal or food you wish to order</p>
    <img src="/images/Grab/MealSelect.jpg" width="300px"><br><br>
    <p>Customize your food according to your preference and press on "Add to Basket" once you are done</p>
    <img src="/images/Grab/Customize meal.jpg" width="300px"><br><br>
    <p>Set by which time you prefer to have your meal dilivered by according to your urgency and choice of spending</p>
    <p>You can add another meal if you desire</p>
    <p>Once everything is done you can press on "Place Order"</p>
    <img src="/images/Grab/TimeSet.jpg" width="300px"><br><br>
    <p>Your Order is now being processed</p>
    <img src = "/images/Grab/OrdProcess.jpg" width="300px"><br><br>
    <p>Your Order is officially done!!!</p>
    <img src = "/images/Grab/OrdComplete.jpg" width="300px"><br><br>
